Attributes.description: Statics of particles, equilibrium or rigid bodies, rigid body statics and internal forces, trusses; kinematics: rectilinear motion; dynamics: Newton's second law, friction, impulse, momentum, work and energy.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: One of PHYS 12, PHYS 100 and one of MATH 100, MATH 102, MATH 104, MATH 110, MATH 120, MATH 180, MATH 184.
Attributes.coreq: Co-reqs: One of MATH 101, MATH 103, MATH 105, MATH 121.
